    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……今日の打ち合わせ、元気がありませんでしたけど\n大丈夫ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You seemed to have less energy during today's meeting.\nAre you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 12.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　大丈夫大丈夫！　ただ緊張しただけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? I'm fine‚ I'm fine! I was just nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに凄いスタッフさん達との仕事なんて\n初めてだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's my first time working with\nsuch an amazing staffs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……本当にただ緊張していただけ、なんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You were really just nervous‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "どういう意味？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせの前から、元気がなかったような気がして\nもしかして、何か悩みごとがあるんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I felt like you weren't energetic even before the meeting started.\nCould it be that you have something on your mind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "……違うと言えば嘘になるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Saying it's not would be a lie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "教えて下さい、何を悩んでるのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please tell me what's bothering you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫\n{user}君に心配はかけたくないしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "t's okay.\nII don't want to trouble you‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "分からない方がもっと心配です\n打ち合わせの進め方に不安があるなら、俺が――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not knowing is even more troubling.\nIf you're worried about how the meeting went‚ I can――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "そういうんじゃないの\n私の気持ちの問題だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not about that.\nIt's a matter of my own feelings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（いつもなら、何かあったらすぐ相談してくれるのに）\n（……俺には言えない悩みなんだろうか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She usually comes to me for advice when something's wrong.）\n（I wonder if there's something she can't tell me…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、バス来たよ。帰ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the bus is here. Let's go home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（……気になるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…I can't help but wonder.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 73
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ、さくらちゃんに任せたMV撮影は\n順調に進んでるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ the MV shoot that we left to Sakura-chan\nis going smoothly‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "アイデアが全ボツを食らって大変でしたが……\nいいMVが出来そうですよ。期待していて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was tough‚ with all the ideas getting rejected…\nWe're on track to make a great MV. Please look forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、楽しみにしてる。私も頑張らないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm looking forward to it. I need to give it my all too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（……遙子さんの悩みを聞き出すきっかけが）\n（見つからないまま、時間だけが過ぎていく……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…The chance to find out what's bothering Haruko-san）\n（…passes by as time keeps ticking…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、{user}君？　ぼーっとしてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay‚ {user}? You seem lost in thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、あのさ。ちょっと気分転換に出かけない？\n夜の散歩。二人で行ってみようよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you know what? How about we go out for refreshing\nAn evening walk. Let's go together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5700.000000000003,
          "startTime": 114.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、こんな時間によく入れてもらえたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ we were lucky to get in at this hour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリの会場に行きたい\nなんて……どうしたんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to go to the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix venue…\nWhat's going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "私にとってここは特別な場所なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This place is special to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。このグランプリで優勝して\n俺達は目が回るほど忙しくなりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. We've been so busy\nsince winning this Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "うん、毎日がすっごく早く進んだよ\nいろんな経験をさせてもらえて、楽しかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ every day went by so fast.\nI had a lot of fun gaining different experiences.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "……私ね\nどうしてもグランプリの決勝に出たかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You know‚\nI really wanted to make it to the Grand Prix finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんが立てなかったステージじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn't a stage for Mana-san‚ was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんほどじゃないけど\n……私にもこだわりがあったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not as much as Kotono-chan‚ of course‚ but…\n…I have my own ego too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君の次に\nアイドル長瀬麻奈を見ていたのは、私だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After you‚ {user}‚\nit was me who watched Idol Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "もっとも私はずっと\n麻奈ちゃんの背中ばかり見てたって感じかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I always felt like\nI kept watching Mana-chan's back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "私は麻奈ちゃんと違って、自分に自信がなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unlike Mana-chan‚ I lacked confidence in myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "途中でアイドルを辞めようかなって考えたり\nずっと心が揺らいでた。ダメだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even thought about quitting being an idol along the way…\nMy heart wavered for a long time. It's no good‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "芸能界は厳しい世界だから、不安になるのは当然です\nでも、遙子さんは人気アイドルになれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's natural to feel anxious in the entertainment industry.\nBut‚ Haruko-san‚ you became a popular idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "本当にそうなのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if that's really true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "今日の打ち合わせで、一流のスタッフさん達を前にして\n私はまた、気持ちがふらふらしちゃったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During today's meeting‚ in front of top-notch staff…\nI felt my emotions waver again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "私より、この場所に立つ資格のある子達が\n他にいるんじゃないかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe there are others who are more deserving to be here…\nSakura-chan and the others can stand on stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん達がいるから、ステージに立ててるだけで\n本当は、もっとふさわしい人がいるのかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "because they're here…\nBut there might be someone more suitable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 224.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……どうしてそんな話をするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why are you talking like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "さっきからずっと私のことを心配してくれてたでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been worried about me all this time‚ haven't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 231.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "だから{user}君には\n私の決断を、ちゃんと伝えておこうと思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I want to properly convey my decision\nto you‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 237.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（……嫌な予感がする。もしかして遙子さんは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…I have a bad feeling. Could it be that Haruko-san…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 242.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-hrk029.m4a",
      "text": "あのね、{user}君\n私決めたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ {user}…\nI've made up my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……まさか\nアイドル、辞めるつもりなんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No way.\nAre you planning to quit being an idol…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.7,
      "sfxList": []
